     The CTs want to hold a spirit revival at a haunted 
house that once was occupied by Hunter S. Thompson.  
Their mission is to extract his Gonzo powers. There 
are two places that might be suitable for the spirit 
revival, the big house, and the cabin in the woods. 
Terrorists, wanting to protect Thompson's dead ass, 
have decided to intervene.

CTs: Eliminate the threat of the terrorist team, 
then perform your spirit revivals.

Ts: Blow up the two locations so there is no chance 
the CTs can hold their spirit revivals. Killing is optional.
